attributes.review: First of all this is a horrible app I don’t recommend it at all too many bugs my phone keeps freezing up it’s just horrible. But the main reason I really want to download this app is because I wanted to see the best presidents of the United States in US history but instead I got a picture of Donald Trump in the homepage and I didn’t like that. And also he told me he was in collect my information like my home address, my shoe size, my shirt size, my pants size, my eye color, my blood type, my weight, and the name of my favorite drink at Starbucks and send it to his best friend in the whole entire world (you know who I’m talking about). Which in fact all of that information is supper classified. Honestly I really don’t recommend this app.
